title: 'Comfortable'
body: I've been using Stayfree pads for a while, and I must say they provide reliable protection and comfort. The pads are absorbent and do an excellent job of keeping me feeling dry and secure during my period. They are also comfortable to wear, with a soft and breathable design. The adhesive stays in place, preventing any shifting or discomfort throughout the day. Overall, Stayfree pads have been a trusted choice for me, offering both effectiveness and comfort during that time of the month.
